  "page": "Rodrik",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Rodrik</b> is a popular male name in Westeros. It may refer to:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Arryn\" title=\"Rodrik Arryn\">Rodrik Arryn</a>, Lord of the Eyrie during the reign of King Jaehaerys I Targaryen</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Cassel\" title=\"Rodrik Cassel\">Rodrik Cassel</a>, the master-at-arms at Winterfell</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Flint\" title=\"Rodrik Flint\">Rodrik Flint</a>, a Lord Commander of the Night's Watch</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Freeborn\" title=\"Rodrik Freeborn\">Rodrik Freeborn</a>, an ironborn raider</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Greyjoy_(son_of_Dalton)\" title=\"Rodrik Greyjoy (son of Dalton)\">Rodrik Greyjoy</a>, a salt son of Lord Dalton Greyjoy</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Greyjoy\" title=\"Rodrik Greyjoy\">Rodrik Greyjoy</a>, eldest son of Lord Balon Greyjoy</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Harlaw\" title=\"Rodrik Harlaw\">Rodrik Harlaw</a>, Lord of Harlaw, Lord of the Ten Towers and head of House Harlaw</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Ryswell\" title=\"Rodrik Ryswell\">Rodrik Ryswell</a>, Lord of the Rills and head of House Ryswell</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Sparr\" title=\"Rodrik Sparr\">Rodrik Sparr</a>, known as \"The Vole\", an ironborn captain</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Stark\" title=\"Rodrik Stark\">Rodrik Stark</a>, a King of Winter</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Stark_(son_of_Beron)\" title=\"Rodrik Stark (son of Beron)\">Rodrik Stark</a>, known as the \"Wandering Wolf\", maternal grandfather of Eddard Stark</li></ul>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Forrester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Rodrik Forrester\">Rodrik Forrester</a>, a character created for the the video game <i>Game of Thrones - A Telltale Games Series</i></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rodrik&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Roderick\" title=\"Roderick\">Roderick</a> (disambiguation)</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404222758\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.004 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.005 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:12494-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404222758 and revision id 323576\n -->\n",
